        <T extends Property<?,?>> void register(Class<T> propertyClass,
                                        PropertyStore<T> propertyStore)
        Registers the provided PropertyStore for the given Property Class. Note that only a single PropertyStore can be registered per Property. Multiple registrations will result in exceptions being thrown.
        Type Parameters:
        T - The type of property
        Parameters:
        propertyClass - The property class
        propertyStore - The property store
